{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he dragged me over to-- he dragged me to the lager-- you know-- alteste.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you know-- for punishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I knew something, you know, not good would happen from this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in the meantime, the lageralteste saw the lagerfuhrer, the German, coming in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he went to greet him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I says-- you know, so I thought to myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If he catch-- I mean, if he comes over, right away, a bullet, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I just snuck away, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were looking and looking and looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, I suppose for some reason or other-- or the lageralteste didn't report it to the lagerfuhrer, you understand?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for some reason or other, it was-- you know, so I was lucky in that particular respect.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, you know, then in February, they started, you know, the Russians started coming closer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were marched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were marched, force marched, you know, to Hirschberg, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was the rainy season.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And snow and sleet and all kind of-- you know, and they were, you know, marching us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people who couldn't-- you know, they were just shooting people on the side, you know, like-- you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, then one particular place we stopped, there were-- you know, they put this into a barn for-- you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a lot of people who tried to run away, or they had an excuse that they were, you know, trying to run away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were shooting right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he was a very sadistic-- you know, this lagerfuhrer was very sadistic.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
